    Class Description
    DescribeProcessReader
    Provides methods to parse a KVP or XML WPS DescribeProcess request and create a DescribeProcessRequest

    Container for WPS DescribeProcess request parameters
    DescribeProcessRequestReader
    Provides methods to parse a KVP or XML WPS DescribeProcess request and create a DescribeProcessRequest

    Provides methods to generate a KVP or XML WPS DescribeProcess request based on values contained in a DescribeProcessRequest object
    DescribeProcessResponse
    container for WPS Describe Process responses with a input/output expressed in SWE Common.
    DescribeProcessResponseReader
    reader for WPS Describe Process responses with a input/output expressed in SWE Common.

    ExecuteProcessRequest
    Container for WPS ExecuteProcess request parameters
    ExecuteProcessRequestWriter
    Writer to write the Execute Process data into the request stream
    ExecuteProcessResponse
    reader for WPS Describe Process responses with a input/output expressed in SWE Common.
    ExecuteProcessResponseReader
    Streaming reader for OM V1.0 responses with a result expressed in SWE Common.
    WPSCapabilitiesReader
    Reads a WPS server capabilities document and create and populate the corresponding OWSServiceCapabilities and WPSLayerCapabilities objects
    WPSLayerCapabilities
    Contains WPS layer capabilities like available formats, requestMode, responseMode...
    WPSUtils
    Utility methods for common stuffs for WPS and SOAP binding and attachment
